character.name: A dignified Islamic religious leader with a bald head and long grey beard. He wears a pristine white robe (thobe) with an embroidered vest and a white kufi cap. Standing in a respectful pose, he holds the Quran with reverence. The pixel art portrays the noble bearing of an imam with clean white garments symbolizing purity and devotion.
